%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Exclusive%20%7C%20Why%20Anand%20withdrew%20from%20Freestyle%20Chess%20GS%20Tour%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738565115000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117879580%2Cimgsize-32524.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fchess%2Fexclusive-why-viswanathan-anand-withdrew-from-freestyle-chess-grand-slam-tour%2Farticleshow%2F117879362.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Viswanathan%20Anand%20has%20pulled%20out%20from%20the%20Freestyle%20Chess%20Grand%20Slam%20Tour.%20His%20new%20role%20as%20FIDE%20Vice%20President%20and%20tensions%20with%20Magnus%20Carlsen%20influenced%20his%20decision.%20The%20tour%20starts%20in%20Germany%20on%20February%207%2C%20with%20top%20players%20like%20Carlsen%20and%20Nakamura%20participating.%20Discussions%20are%20ongoing%20about%20the%20New%20Delhi%20leg%20and%20the%20use%20of%20the%20term%20'World%20Championship'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22JYOTIRMOY%20HALDER%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bill%20Gates%20said%20he%20did%20his%20best%20to%20save%20things%20like%20funding%20for%20HIV%20research%20during%20a%203-hour%20meeting%20with%20Trump%20at%20Mar-a-Lago%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bill%20Gates%20speaking%20at%20the%20%26quot%3BWorld%20Health%20Summit%26quot%3B%20conference%3B%20Donald%20Trump%20speaking%20to%20reporters%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a02d74eb4be2fff9a33732%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20his%20ear%20for%20three%20hours.%20He%20couldn't%20have%20been%20nicer%2C%26quot%3B%20Bill%20Gates%20said%20of%20his%20meeting%20with%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20after%20Christmas.%3Cp%3EAnnette%20Riedl%20via%20Getty%20Images%3B%20Chip%20Somodevilla%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBill%20Gates%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bhad%20a%20really%20good%2C%20very%20long%20dinner%26quot%3B%20with%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20last%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGates%20said%20he%20told%20Trump%20to%20retain%20PEPFAR%2C%20a%20long-running%20foreign%20aid%20program%20that%20combats%20HIV.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20halting%20all%20foreign%20aid%20programs%20for%2090%20days%20after%20he%20was%20sworn%20in.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gates%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBill%20Gates%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he%20pushed%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20maintain%20America's%20aid%20and%20relief%20programs%20for%20HIV%20during%20a%20meeting%20they%20had%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGates%20told%20The%20New%20Yorker's%20editor%20David%20Remnick%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorker.com%2Fpodcast%2Fthe-new-yorker-radio-hour%2Fbill-gates-on-his-new-memoir-and-dining-with-donald-trump-at-mar-a-lago%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20Sunday%2C%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bhad%20a%20really%20good%2C%20very%20long%20dinner%26quot%3B%20with%20Trump%20at%20Mar-a-Lago%20after%20Christmas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%2C%20we%20talked%20about%20the%20world%20broadly%2C%20but%20my%20first%20request%20was%20on%20HIV%2C%20where%20there's%20a%20question%20of%20whether%20the%20US%20maintains%20the%20PEPFAR%20program%20that's%20over%20twenty%20years%20standing%2C%20that%20keeps%20over%20ten%20million%20people%20alive%20with%20HIV%20medicines%2C%26quot%3B%20Gates%20told%20Remnick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPEPFAR%2C%20or%20the%20President's%20Emergency%20Plan%20for%20AIDS%20Relief%2C%20is%20a%20foreign%20aid%20program%20that%20was%20started%20by%20then-President%20George%20W.%20Bush%20in%202003.%20The%20program%20has%20saved%2026%20million%20lives%20and%20prevented%20millions%20of%20HIV%20infections%20around%20the%20world%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fpepfar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EState%20Department%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20funding%20for%20PEPFAR%20was%20paused%20on%20January%2020%2C%20after%20Trump%20signed%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fpresidential-actions%2F2025%2F01%2Freevaluating-and-realigning-united-states-foreign-aid%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexecutive%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20freezing%20all%20foreign%20aid%20programs%20for%2090%20days%20until%20they%20are%20reviewed.%20According%20to%20the%20State%20Department%2C%20the%20US%20has%20given%20over%20%24110%20billion%20in%20funding%20to%20PEPFAR.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20his%20ear%20for%20three%20hours.%20He%20couldn't%20have%20been%20nicer.%20Doesn't%20mean%20that%20other%20people%20won't%20come%20in%20and%20say%20the%20HIV%20money%20should%20be%20cut%2C%20but%20I%20did%20my%20best%2C%26quot%3B%20Gates%20said%20of%20his%20meeting%20with%20Trump%20in%20his%20interview%20with%20The%20New%20Yorker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unclear%20what%20will%20become%20of%20PEPFAR%20under%20Trump.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20announced%20a%20waiver%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Femergency-humanitarian-waiver-to-foreign-assistance-pause%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efor%20life-saving%20humanitarian%20assistance%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20to%20Trump's%20executive%20order%20on%20foreign%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20resumption%20is%20temporary%20in%20nature%2C%20and%20with%20limited%20exceptions%20as%20needed%20to%20continue%20life-saving%20humanitarian%20assistance%20programs%2C%20no%20new%20contracts%20shall%20be%20entered%20into%2C%26quot%3B%20Rubio%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Femergency-humanitarian-waiver-to-foreign-assistance-pause-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGates%20has%20spent%20resources%20on%20philanthropic%20causes%20like%20climate%20change%20and%20global%20health%20since%20stepping%20down%20as%20CEO%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20software%20giant%20he%20cofounded%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-fabulous-life-of-paul-allen-2014-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPaul%20Allen%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%201975.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGates%20was%20Microsoft's%20CEO%20until%202000%2C%20and%20was%20its%20chairman%20until%202014.%20He%20left%20Microsoft's%20board%20in%202020.%20Gates%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fpulse%2Ffocusing-my-time-bill-gates%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March%202020%20that%20stepping%20down%20from%20the%20board%20would%20allow%20him%20%26quot%3Bto%20dedicate%20more%20time%20to%20philanthropic%20priorities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gatesfoundation.org%2Fabout%2Ffoundation-fact-sheet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGates%20Foundation's%3C%2Fa%3E%20website%2C%20Gates%20and%20his%20former%20wife%2C%20Melinda%20French%20Gates%2C%20have%20given%20%2459.5%20billion%20to%20the%20foundation%20since%20its%20inception%20in%202000.%20French%20Gates%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmelinda-french-gates-resigns-from-gates-foundation-charity-bill-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleft%20the%20foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20June%2C%20three%20years%20after%20she'd%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%