f_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40IndiGo6E%3C%2Fa%3E%20needs%20to%20be%20held%20accountable%20for%20the%20pathetic%20downfall%20in%20its%20service!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHere's%20what%20went%20down%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Dr.%20Datta%20MD%20(AIIMS%20Delhi)%20(%40DrDatta_AIIMS)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrDatta_AIIMS%2Fstatus%2F1886048880686723492%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%202%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recounted%20the%20flight%20took%20off%20around%203%3A30%20pm%2C%20and%20soon%20after%2C%20the%20meal%20service%20began.%20When%20the%20crew%20reached%20his%20seat%2C%20they%20informed%20him%20that%20his%20pre-booked%20meal%20might%20be%20delayed%20due%20to%20an%20issue%20at%20Bangalore%20airport.%20Initially%20understanding%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20Mr%20Datta%20patiently%20waited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%2030%20minutes%20of%20silence%20from%20the%20crew%2C%20he%20followed%20up%20and%20was%20told%20that%20another%20crew%20member%20would%20assist%20him.%20Yet%2C%20no%20one%20came%20forward.%20As%20time%20passed%2C%20he%20started%20feeling%20the%20effects%20of%20hypoglycemia%20-%20deficiency%20of%20glucose%20in%20the%20bloodstream.%20He%20was%20%E2%80%9Cgrowing%20increasingly%20irritated%20and%20jittery%E2%80%9D%20while%20the%20flight%20crew%20continued%20to%20ignore%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%204%3A00%20pm%2C%20a%20fellow%20passenger%20noticed%20his%20distress%20and%20offered%20him%20her%20sandwich%2C%20but%20by%20then%2C%20his%20frustration%20had%20peaked.%20In%20an%20attempt%20to%20get%20assistance%2C%20he%20pressed%20the%20emergency%20call%20button.%20Still%2C%20no%20crew%20members%20responded%20for%20nearly%20half%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20breaking%20point%E2%80%9D%20for%20him%20was%20when%20the%20aircraft%20began%20its%20descent%20and%20the%20captain%20announced%20that%20the%20flight%20was%20nearing%20Delhi.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20the%20doctor%20had%20still%20not%20received%20his%20pre-booked%20meal%2C%20nor%20had%20anyone%20attended%20to%20his%20emergency%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTheir%20complete%20indifference%20was%20infuriating%20and%20made%20me%20think%3A%20What%20if%20this%20neglect%20put%20someone%20in%20a%20real%20medical%20emergency%20in%20danger%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20around%205%3A40%20pm%20%E2%80%93%20more%20than%20two%20hours%20after%20takeoff%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20crew%20finally%20approached%20him.%20He%20reminded%20them%20that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpre-diabetic%20and%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20receiving%20my%20meal%20on%20time%E2%80%9D.%20The%20airline%20staff%20then%20handed%20him%20his%20sandwich%20but%20with%20another%20mistake%20%E2%80%93%20he%20had%20requested%20black%20tea%20(without%20sugar)%20but%20was%20instead%20given%20black%20coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20that%20time%20I%20was%20so%20hypoglycaemic%20that%20I%20did%20not%20even%20have%20the%20energy%20or%20strength%20to%20argue!%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Datta%20was%20particularly%20outraged%20by%20how%20the%20airline%20disregarded%20his%20emergency%20call%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20lack%20of%20response%20made%20him%20question%20how%20IndiGo%20would%20handle%20an%20actual%20medical%20emergency%20mid-flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20passengers%20pay%20for%20their%20services%20and%20deserve%20basic%20respect.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20flying%20for%20free!%20We%20pay%20for%20our%20tickets%20and%20services.%20IndiGo's%20crew%20displayed%20an%20appalling%20level%20of%20unprofessionalism%20and%20arrogance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20post%2C%20he%20revealed%20that%20he%20had%20recorded%20all%20conversations%20with%20timestamps%20and%20was%20prepared%20to%20escalate%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20National%20Consumer%20Disputes%20Redressal%20Commission%20(NCDRC).%20He%20also%20urged%20others%20who%20faced%20similar%20issues%20with%20IndiGo%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20him%2C%20as%20he%20was%20considering%20legal%20action%20to%20push%20the%20airline%20to%20improve%20its%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20social%20media%20backlash%2C%20IndiGo%20issued%20an%20official%20response%20to%20Mr%20Datta's%20post.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20sincerely%20apologise%20for%20the%20delay%20in%20serving%20your%20pre-booked%20meal%20and%20the%20inconvenience%20this%20caused%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20airline%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3Eand%20prioritising%20our%20customers'%20needs%20and%20comfort.%20Please%20be%20assured%20that%20we%20take%20your%20feedback%20seriously%20and%20have%20taken%20the%20necessary%20steps%20to%20prevent%20a%20recurrence.%20We%20truly%20appreciate%20your%20patience%20and%20look%20forward%20to%20the%20opportunity%20of%20serving%20you%20on%20your%20next%20journey.%20(2%2F2)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20IndiGo%20(%40IndiGo6E)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIndiGo6E%2Fstatus%2F1886244217267142735%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%203%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20IndiGo%2C%20we%20are%20committed%20to%20understanding%20and%20prioritising%20our%20customers'%20needs%20and%20comfort.%20Please%20be%20assured%20that%20we%20take%20your%20feedback%20seriously%20and%20have%20taken%20the%20necessary%20steps%20to%20prevent%20a%20recurrence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738560240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-01%2F0kgrkpeo_indigo-generic_625x300_16_January_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fex-aiims-delhi-doctor-slams-indigo-over-nightmare-flight-experience-airline-responds-7621647%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Suvrankar%20Datta%2C%20who%20said%20he%20was%20a%20pre-diabetic%2C%20claimed%20IndiGo%20failed%20to%20serve%20his%20booked%20meal%20on%20tim