C%20the%20Mexican%20Chamber%20of%20the%20Tequila%20Industry%2C%20and%20Spirits%20Canada%2C%20said%20the%20implementation%20of%20tariffs%20threatens%20the%20growth%20of%20trade%20in%20spirits%20across%20the%20three%20countries%2C%20a%20major%20issue%20given%20setbacks%20related%20to%20COVID-19%20and%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20associations%20are%20committed%20to%20working%20collaboratively%20with%20all%20stakeholders%20to%20explore%20solutions%20that%20prevent%20potential%20tariffs%20on%20distilled%20spirits%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20groups%20said%20in%20their%20statement.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20deeply%20concerned%20that%20US%20tariffs%20on%20imported%20spirits%20from%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20will%20significantly%20harm%20all%20three%20countries%20and%20lead%20to%20a%20cycle%20of%20retaliatory%20tariffs%20that%20negatively%20impacts%20our%20shared%20industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaintaining%20fair%20and%20reciprocal%20duty-free%20access%20for%20all%20distilled%20spirits%20is%20crucial%20for%20supporting%20jobs%20and%20shared%20growth%20across%20North%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eb3627b4-ffad-40d2-b260-c960741b3aa7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmerican%20Automotive%20Policy%20Council%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMatt%20Blunt%2C%20former%20governor%20of%20Missouri%20and%20president%20of%20the%20American%20Automotive%20Policy%20Council%2C%20which%20represents%20Ford%20Motor%2C%20General%20Motors%2C%20and%20Stellantis%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20he%20doesn't%20believe%20that%20vehicles%20and%20parts%20that%20meet%20the%20USMCA's%20requirements%20%E2%80%94%20agreed%20upon%20by%20the%20US%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20Mexico%20in%202020%20%E2%80%94%20should%20be%20subject%20to%20increased%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20American%20automakers%2C%20who%20invested%20billions%20in%20the%20US%20to%20meet%20these%20requirements%2C%20should%20not%20have%20their%20competitiveness%20undermined%20by%20tariffs%20that%20will%20raise%20the%20cost%20of%20building%20vehicles%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20stymie%20investment%20in%20the%20American%20workforce%2C%26quot%3B%20Blunt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221a0f2bce-47a3-4c02-930d-34e2c56e7f8b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECanadian%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECandace%20Laing%2C%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20Canadian%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%2C%20representing%20more%20than%20200%2C000%20businesses%2C%20called%20Trump's%20tariffs%20%26quot%3Bself-defeating%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bprofoundly%20disturbing%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20supply%20chains%20are%20so%20deeply%20integrated%20that%20you%20can't%20unwind%20them%20overnight%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Laing%2C%20%26quot%3BWhich%20is%20why%20if%20President%20Trump%20truly%20wanted%20to%20bring%20down%20costs%20for%20Americans%2C%20he%20would%20be%20looking%20at%20strengthening%20our%20trade%20ties%2C%20not%20tearing%20them%20apart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaing%20recounted%20how%20the%20US%20relies%20on%20Canadian%20imports%2C%20such%20as%20crude%20oil%20and%20critical%20minerals%2C%20and%20said%20that%20Canada's%20%26quot%3Bjob%20number%20one%26quot%3B%20right%20now%20is%20to%20build%20resilience%20and%20provide%20security%20to%20Canadian%20families%20and%20businesses%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Brightly%20scared%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20can't%20trade%20south%2C%20let's%20diversify%20our%20trading%20partners%20and%20dismantle%20unnecessary%20internal%20trade%20barriers%20to%20keep%20goods%20and%20services%20flowing%20north%2C%20east%2C%20and%20west%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20strong%2C%20united%2C%20and%20competitive%20Canadian%20economy%20will%20thrive%20no%20matter%20what%20gets%20thrown%20our%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dc31677e-670b-49ff-8cf5-fcb02e61219c%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Petroleum%20Institute%3C%2Fh2%3E%