0the%20country%20began%20preparing%20themselves%20for%20an%20onslaught%20of%20conservative-driven%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20new%20year%20began%2C%20Democrats%20in%20the%20states%20filed%20a%20flurry%20of%20bills%20addressing%20everything%20from%20minimum%20wage%20increases%20and%20price%20fixing%20to%20child%20poverty%20and%20medical%20leave%20to%20stave%20off%20Trump's%20expected%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20preparation%2C%20Democrats%20were%20still%20alarmed%2C%20however%2C%20when%20the%20administration%20last%20week%20sought%20to%20freeze%20billions%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-house-temporarily-froze-all-federal-grants-and-loans-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efederal%20funding%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20state%20Democrats%20are%20seeking%20to%20advance%20their%20priorities%20against%20the%20prospect%20of%20federal%20funding%20fights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e3f4f864-bd4b-4fa4-bea1-b78a341afed8%5C%22%3EAn%20eye%20on%20housing%20affordability%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20campaign%20success%20rested%20largely%20on%20the%20economy%2C%20rallying%20his%20base%20and%20even%20some%20longtime%20Democratic%20voters%20to%20the%20GOP%20over%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20potential%20of%20a%20funding%20freeze%2C%20however%2C%20could%20threaten%20critical%20housing%20assistance%20programs%20that%20have%20aided%20many%20Americans.%20The%20president's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-plan-deadline-trade-policies-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20imports%20from%20Canada%2C%20China%2C%20and%20Mexico%20could%20also%20raise%20the%20cost%20of%20materials%20for%20construction%2C%20causing%20house%20prices%20to%20go%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20Democrats%20in%20the%20states%20are%20trying%20to%20pass%20a%20series%20of%20laws%20focused%20on%20housing%20affordability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20